de Slaaptimer in, zodat de projector na een bepaalde tijd (1 uur \/ 2 uur \/ 4 uur) automatisch wordt uitgeschakeld.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19997927637316__fd1d3b17-b523-4b70-9445-515fd1e30f38-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":12}},"b1b86534-b40b-47e5-b52f-6f3ae7a23194":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_4_g.png","height":"medium","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"f825b17c-d0af-43fc-a271-1843811594cb":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19997927637316__f825b17c-d0af-43fc-a271-1843811594cb-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Onze projector is uitsluitend gemaakt met <strong>geselecteerde <\/strong>en <strong>milieuvriendelijke <\/strong>componenten.<\/p><p>Elk apparaat ondergaat een reeks <strong>veeleisende controles en tests<\/strong> in een overeenstemming met Europese specificaties voordat het onze fabriek verlaat.<\/p><p>Zo garanderen wij u veiligheid, robuustheid, lange levensduur en duurzaamheid<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19997927637316__f825b17c-d0af-43fc-a271-1843811594cb-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":12}},"26469175-7bd6-4300-83f3-66dcb2660016":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--19997927637316__26469175-7bd6-4300-83f3-66dcb2660016-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>Pakketsinhoud<\/h3>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["template--19997927637316__26469175-7bd6-4300-83f3-66dcb2660016-text-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/4_ddingen_gif.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section